9.4&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&ldquo;unique application numbers&rdquo;:&nbsp; Certain services include a unique application number. This number and information about your installation (for example, the operating system type and application version number) may be sent to us when you install or uninstall such a service or when that service periodically contacts our servers, such as for automatic updates.&nbsp;</div>

