	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</li>
	<li style="font-size: 1em; outline: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">MultiChoice Africa (Pty (Ltd) and MultiChoice Operations (Pty) Ltd&ndash; 251 Oak Avenue, Randburg, South Africa; &nbsp;</li>
